skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This is skill is all about helping you to LIVE the real estate life. Everyone is invited to listen, real estate agents, real estate brokers, lenders, buyers, sellers, landlords, tenants, and anyone else that wants to LIVE the real estate life. 
Listen to weekly updates from your favorite real estate broker associate from Texas. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
